question: How much has the VIEIX fund increased its net asset value since 2 years ago
expected_cypher:
MATCH (f:Fund {ticker: 'VIEIX'})-[r:HAS_FINANCIAL_HIGHLIGHT]->(fh:FinancialHighlight)
WITH fh, r.year AS year
ORDER BY year DESC
LIMIT 2
WITH collect(fh) AS highlights
WHERE size(highlights) = 2
WITH highlights[0] AS latest, highlights[1] AS two_years_ago
RETURN 
    latest.netAssetsValueEnd AS currentNAV,
    two_years_ago.netAssetsValueEnd AS previousNAV,
    (latest.netAssetsValueEnd - two_years_ago.netAssetsValueEnd) AS absoluteIncrease,
    ((latest.netAssetsValueEnd - two_years_ago.netAssetsValueEnd) / two_years_ago.netAssetsValueEnd) * 100 AS percentageGrowth
